GUI

Class PanelCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • GUI.PanelCreator

  • public class PanelCreator
extends java.lang.Object
    The class PanelCreator is the second most important class of the GUI. It creates the frame and all the panels and menu bars. For each panel and menu bars, it associates each button with a listener of the Launch class.
    Author:
    jeremyaugot, maxspahn
